Nick Loeb has filed a lawsuit in California to prevent Sofia Vergara from destroying two cryopreserved female embryos created through IVF . 
  Court documents claim the couple fertilized embryos using her eggs and his sperm six months before their split in November 2013 . 
  Loeb is seeking to ensure the female embryos are not destroyed . 
  He also claims the actress was 'physically and mentally abusive' to him . 
  The Modern Family actress is now engaged to Joe Manganiello . 
 